&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Full time employees receive an above market total compensation package along with employee-led remote and flexible working, health benefits, Samsara for Good charity fund, and much, much more. Take a look at our &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.samsara.com/company/careers/benefits&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Benefits&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;site to learn more.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
