&lt;li&gt;Identify risks to growth goals and develop action plans to mitigate those risks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support quarterly business activities and development of executive materials (executive briefing memos, sales kickoff slides, business reviews, and executive presentations)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
